thread.title: Mark

author: Mark
title: Mark
text:
So far I have only purchased a few things for my gts300. It was a first class service from start to finish. My parts arrived quickly and well packed to protect them.
My only concern was due to the exchange rate I was paying more than I was expecting. It was only a few pounds as I live in the U.K. This will not put me off using them again though. I emailed them regarding this and got a swift reply explaining why. I look forward to buying more parts in the future.
